# Change laptop behaviour when lid is closed
```bash
sudo nvim /etc/systemd/logind.conf
```
change `HandleLidSwitch` and `HandleLidSwitchExternalPower` to one of the following:

- lock
- ignore
- poweroff
- hibernate
- suspend

